Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像是沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎也不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…我倒覺得不是什麼大事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打過手機了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像關機了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一…出了什麼事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不必那麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一下  沒頭沒腦地去找也不是辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩托起火了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貸款還有很多沒有付清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像挺美的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得去買女式自行車去打工…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頭疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽油燒著了也不會爆炸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了  那種事只有在電影裡才會有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如乾脆轟隆一下  然後一了百了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錢叫出租車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題在於能不能叫到出租車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個都沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不叫救護車沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要報告給警察  好好處理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒有受傷真是不幸中的萬幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼？老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓女人們在一起會更好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡給比呂美灌輸些奇怪的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那難道是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美和我是親兄妹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換衣服吧  我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事是不可能的  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽  比呂美  你們在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在吧  我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽  我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服都髒兮兮的  我要換衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那過會兒再說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  媽媽你太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸登上後院的土堤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  約有十米的巨大的土堤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那裡看到的地面的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿就是地底一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在啄食餌食的地面看起來很淒慘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  飛翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸雖然是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那時肚子卻咕嚕咕嚕地叫著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終  它決定今天還是放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定明天吃飽餌食後再去天空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還是飛不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.79,0:09:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美  今天都吃些什麼菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼體貼人  一點都不像朋與
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:10:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好友是個如此震撼校園的大醜聞的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這區區一介女子高中生角色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也夠嗆的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  要是連你都在意的話該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為那樣  我才沒有面子的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先告訴你一下消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在召開職員會議
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,題目是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於本校數一數二的高材生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籃球部的王牌  端莊秀麗並且眉清目秀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端莊秀麗和眉清目秀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算啦  吃飯吧吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  今天交換的份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去了湯淺比呂美的事故現場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:10:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說4號那傢伙也沒受傷？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  真是個走運的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  仲上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是哥們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師都那樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高岡隊長什麼時候變成規章制度的維護者了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說停學那也是從明天才開始的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請允許我也退出今天的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去陪著比呂美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美和朋與的份也要給我算進去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  沒有記錯的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說「我喜歡乃繪」  還在這裡寫下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗茶淡飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打架咯  打架咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  打死他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才真是把我嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥說停學一周
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  搞出這麼大的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有必要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了湯淺比呂美才打架的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  還好嗎 地面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連環畫的後續畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美是我們的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會負責管教她的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸不太容易飛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸也隱隱約約感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  即使從十米高的土堤上開始飛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是哪也去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一直在裝作不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼雷轟丸不面對現實？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是…害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢面對自己只是區區一隻雞這個現實
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸其實從一開始就知道自己是飛不起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也指真一郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼  好疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎  你能飛翔的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是自己不知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你翱翔的地方不是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.35,0:19:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我和伯父伯母一起從學校回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去學校了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰…冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回家路上和伯母買的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君的在冰箱裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:19:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道沒有那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「你是我丈夫的孩子」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些話都是騙人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你見到不成體統的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些話都是騙人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前對你太刻薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來也知道伯母不喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人之間存在著稱為緣分的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那個和這個是兩碼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你忘記以前發生過的所有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那的確是太自以為是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡多待一會兒可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那曲子我以前常聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我像個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.91,0:21:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸地陷入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸地  漸漸地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是該說謝謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.64,0:23:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會全部處理好的
